<p>This guy seems pretty lax for being a demoted Foundation personnel, with the fucks and the not really freaking out about being a D-class personnel suddenly. Amnesiacs or whatever fine..</p>
<p>200 meters is a decent guess, but then the team also concludes it sounds to be 200 meters below? And it's in the documentation as sound like it's 200 meters below? Too spot on. What? Did they just take the first number the heard and run with it?</p>
<p>The line about this face without pupils making direct eye contact is bugging me. Sure we can assume it is watching someone by it facing them directly and not blinking, but can we really say that it's making eye contact? No, I do not think so since that act requires pupils to be looking at each other.</p>

